DEG vs DFC

res_ <- res %>% mutate(log10FDR=-log(padj,10),PN=(log2FoldChange>0)) %>% left_join(.,Wei[,c(1,4)],by="ext_gene")
res_$class[is.na(res_$weight)] <- "nonDFC"
Unknown or uninitialised column: `class`.
res_$class[res_$weight!="nonDFC"] <- "DFC"
ggplot(res_,aes(x=log2FoldChange,y=log10FDR,color=class)) + geom_point(size=1.2,alpha=0.6) + theme_minimal() + scale_color_manual(values = c("#D62728FF","#808080")) 

ggplot(res_,aes(x=baseMean,y=log2FoldChange,color=class)) + geom_point(size=0.8,alpha=0.8) + theme_minimal() + scale_color_manual(values = c("#D62728FF","#808080")) + scale_x_log10()
